<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>画像</title>
</head>
<body>

<img src="./bg0.png" alt="背景"><br>

<div style="position: absolute; left: 20px; top: 20px; background: #fef3c7; padding: 6px;">
  ぽかぽか陽気の穏やかな朝<br>
  花畑には、蝶々がのびのび飛んでいます
</div>

<div style="position: relative; width: 30px; height: 20px;">
  <img src="./butterfly.gif" style="position: absolute; left: 40px; top: -200px;">
</div>

<div style="position: relative; width: 30px; height: 20px;">
  <img src="./butterfly.gif" style="position: absolute; left: 500px; top: -180px;">
</div>

</body>
</html>
